headline: From the Court to Commerce: Tennis Champion Rafael Nadal to Headline VTEX Connect Europe 2025
summary: NEW YORK, October 14, 2025--VTEX (NYSE: VTEX), the sole Customers’ Choice commerce platform for two years by Gartner® and trusted by global brands including Colgate, Stanley Black & Decker, and Whirlpool, announces that 22-time Grand Slam tennis champion and entrepreneur Rafael Nadal, will headline VTEX Connect Europe on November 11, 2025, at Pavilhão Carlos Lopes in Lisbon, Portugal.
